    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should talk to someone, but what’s the point? everyone just tells me to \"keep trying\" or \"take a break,\" but they don't get it. it’s not even a mood or a bad day. it's like the essence of me—the thing that made me me—is just dead. there's no light left in the room. i'm just a walking corpse, existing for no reason.",
